prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration of the couple from the reference photo, transformed into simple cartoon characters. The scene is a funny depiction of them skiing down a gentle, clean white snowy hill. Lao Lao, on the right, is skiing confidently with a huge smile, effortlessly balancing a large boba tea in one hand like a pro. Jordan, on the left, is in a comically clumsy pose, skis tangled, looking slightly panicked but laughing as he's about to fall over, with his own boba tea splashing mid-air. They are wearing cozy, minimalist ski outfits. The background is a simple, soft pastel blue sky with a few elegant, clean lines indicating the snowy slope. In the center, in a beautiful, elegant, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao". Clean lines, solid colors, ample negative space.
